Package display

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CovidTracker
    The CovidTrakcer is a Display that keeps track of the number of Covid cases in each Tier
    Display
    The Display class represents an object that is displayed on the window
    GameComponent
    Represents a component on the grid of a Tier
    Inventory
    The Inventory class is a Display that shows what the player has
    Location
    Represents the location of a person in the Tier
    Map
    The Map class is a Display which represents the map of California and boxes which are both interactive.
    Menu
    The Menu class is a Display that represents the options that the user has regarding the program
    TaskBar
    The TaskBar class represents a Display that gives the user recommended tasks to complete in each Tier.
    Tier
    This class represents the overall structure of a Tier, or level, in the Mask On! game
    TimerDisplay
    The TimerDisplay class is a Display that represents a stopwatch used to keep track of how much time the user spends on a Tier
